snippet.title: EQQO - Nintendo Switch™ Trailer
snippet.description:
Unravel the threads of a poetic puzzle-adventure inspired by nature and Ethiopian mythology!

Available in English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Brazilian Portuguese, Russian, Chinese, Japanese and Korean!

EQQO was released in February on Nintendo Switch™: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/eqqo-switch/
It will also come to PC eventually.

It's already available in VR: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/go/2461352513879642/
And on Android smartphones: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ParallelStudio.EQQOMOBILE

EQQO is created by Parallel Studio and published by Nakana.io.

Don't want to miss any news from Nakana.io?

Or join on Discord: https://discord.gg/ZSYjjRW
